**Summary:** Documents timezone-related data discrepancies between Amplitude charts, Snowflake/Redshift destinations, and Export API, explaining that Snowflake and Export API use UTC timezone while Amplitude charts use project timezone settings, and Export API date ranges are based on server_upload_time rather than event_time.

